data.description: Charming, 3 bed/2 bath, 1400+ sqft home with lots of natural sunlight is nestled in a sprawling corner lot.  With a cozy dining room, kitchen and strainless steel appliances,  there's also extra space for a den or rec area and bonus room for storage or office.  The timeless all brick exterior, fenced in backyard and huge 2-car garage bring everything together to complete this home.  Enjoy great restaurants, fun events and unique shops in downtown Indy just 15 minutes away.  Make new memories with family and friends in this lovely home! Selling As-Is. Property is part of an estate.
